longBusinessSummary: Transtema Group AB installs, maintains, and manages the operation of various communication networks in the Nordic region. The company offers operation and maintenance services, such as network monitoring, consulting, support, site, data center, site management, and field services; communication network, including fiber, mobile, copper network, property network, IoT, wireless networks, mobile indoor coverage, telecommunication system, and network equipment; and charging infrastructure comprising electricity car charging, charging stations, charging boxes, and charging station services. It also provides networking equipment, data storage, IoT solutions. Transtema Group AB was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Mölndal, Sweden.
